{"tid":2404312,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"【術式反轉】","createTime":"2021-02-11T15:43:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T02:37:00.000Z","uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"02cd913842a11fcc47ef77d13423b7dd3a0b3f20","tid":2404312,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T15:43:49.000Z","msg":"我的術式。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d47956d87a2f7015ff891a469f973665b26c8361","tid":2404312,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T15:45:08.000Z","msg":"我只是想成為強大的咒術師。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1f00c6cdd22f9cbddadf532bcdc1e332184bb02","tid":2404312,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T16:24:25.000Z","msg":"這些東西都建立一場對我的不完全的謀殺之上。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我的術式。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61e6c12a8138cac7ed9b5f50eeb2ab4e86ac3f6d","tid":2404312,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T16:33:00.000Z","msg":"有一天，他暴露了自己的本性，對我進行謀殺。但最後只把我打成重傷。第二天，我仍然繼續面對這些殺人犯，明明連命都差點沒了，以為自己在積極地生活。對自己說，過去的事都過去了！其實真相過去被謀殺，而謀殺的犯人仍在我面前。其實他有機會，仍然會謀殺我。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"909f235867b2839faed0b7f8e5ad87cb68f27068","tid":2404312,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T16:34:20.000Z","msg":"對方想謀殺我，我再改變自己，對方依然會想謀殺我。"},{"pid":"c0482ffac02c1e22bd6ebbd870ee6995fd2d87d1","tid":2404312,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T16:37:43.000Z","msg":"他只是在做自己想做的事，而根本不在乎我是甚麼人。"},{"pid":"9d5780117b7caca858da70a5d6fecb203956d5ba","tid":2404312,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T16:39:25.000Z","msg":"卻仍在浪費時間聽謀殺犯說話。"},{"pid":"493a164892e388cd7655cb0c173257e4e31b695f","tid":2404312,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T16:40:15.000Z","msg":"可是他真的嘗試要謀殺我呀。。。為甚麼我仍然呆呆地對着他。。。"},{"pid":"af11e50f153c1a4e989cb07112b075864608f079","tid":2404312,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T16:45:33.000Z","msg":"好後悔。對方明明是謀殺犯，而且都出過手了。我不知還對着他做甚麼。還有其他人，其實都謀殺犯的同伴。他明明己經要殺死我了，而其他人的而且確很認同殺人犯，支持他的殺人活動。<br />\n<br />\n我卻仍要&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1adada79abf538fe979d7cecf59dd7479c0c305f","tid":2404312,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T16:48:11.000Z","msg":"如果有一個人，曾經謀殺我，而他身邊有很多熟人，支持他的殺人行為。<br />\n<br />\n那我應該因為那些人沒有直接參與謀殺，而相信「社交」這回事，去和他「社交」嗎？"},{"pid":"37e226eae911ce5fe80644acba3cba15aa4131be","tid":2404312,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T16:51:46.000Z","msg":"有一些人謀殺我了。<br />\n<br />\n但我發現，這些謀殺我的人，有很多支持者。<br />\n<br />\n我應該只避開謀殺我的人。<br />\n<br />\n還是要連同謀殺犯的支持者一起，全避開呢？"},{"pid":"c716cd075a2fa4c224285e47daa570871b331671","tid":2404312,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T16:53:03.000Z","msg":"假如我要連同謀殺犯的支持者一起避開，那這些支持者的支持者，我也要避開嗎？"},{"pid":"90e9295605720c003fde2572af46dd8f1c724d0b","tid":2404312,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T16:54:47.000Z","msg":"對的，當然要避開了。謀殺犯就是謀殺犯，謀殺犯的支持者也支持謀殺，支持者的支持者也支持支持謀殺。<br />\n<br />\n都想我死的。我又怎能不避開，想死嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"909516c79d73713b70435ada9590e8879b6dcfb0","tid":2404312,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T17:00:20.000Z","msg":"我被謀殺了，卻一直解決不了謀殺犯。這些人就當謀殺這回事不存在，開始說我怎樣怎樣。。。。。。被謀殺的我，又能怎樣做呢。。。。。。"},{"pid":"15a9e515eac404fde8b2f01669aeb082ae67aaf2","tid":2404312,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T17:03:58.000Z","msg":"這個世界，會一邊支持謀殺，然後一邊說要開解被謀殺的人，然後一邊支持别人繼續謀殺被謀殺的人。這樣就可以揾食了。"},{"pid":"b078d1c950fb3de241ab7323d4aea03e62a42fbb","tid":2404312,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T17:05:14.000Z","msg":"社工這職業，就是首先把人弄個半死，再開始幫助你，不然要怎樣揾食呀？"},{"pid":"e730786a0e6162e51b421f2b1f660e9f3d122ace","tid":2404312,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T17:05:54.000Z","msg":"不先把人弄得半死，我怎麼工作？我不就要失業了？"},{"pid":"be2969cbaef54f3c1fbd6a5e50cb5a5b3483c3d8","tid":2404312,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T17:06:39.000Z","msg":"教師也是一樣，不把你弄不懂，我怎麼教懂你？要怎麼揾食呀。。。"},{"pid":"27a3f40a8eb9c67f8e7c08e1d85d61dde06005bb","tid":2404312,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T17:08:56.000Z","msg":"mum and dad, why you一直都唔同我講真相？"},{"pid":"12e2493bd10b31b9ef601a1c1bfcf6cadcde5cb6","tid":2404312,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T17:12:46.000Z","msg":"就是故意製造麻煩，然後說要解決麻煩，其實是在裝忙。你真的相信嗎？你才15歲，相信就算了。都已經50歲了，還相信？真相呢？"},{"pid":"efd5b09a8bfefeaa4448019fd27e0f8ad690526f","tid":2404312,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T17:14:56.000Z","msg":"就是故意製造麻煩，然後說要解決麻煩，其實就是要裝得很忙很辛苦的樣子，來騙飯食而己。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />怎麼可能相信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6136b0aebb52b5cf7d3f4f9b44aa995c7d6b1b4c","tid":2404312,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T17:18:25.000Z","msg":"就是故意製造麻煩，然後說要解決麻煩，這樣就可以裝得很忙很辛苦的樣子，來騙飯食。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />别再騙人了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />怎麼可能相信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30d01eccfe57b619318c9d989f35eadcd8a42f52","tid":2404312,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T17:21:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我的術式<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"579f5d7bdb9efa8ea7a94d273a11338a6a83d098","tid":2404312,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T17:25:09.000Z","msg":"就像那些詛呪師，先在有錢人身上下咒，再說幫你解咒，每次解咒收一大筆錢，解完再下，下完再解，解完再收錢，收錢完再下，下完再解，解完再收錢，這樣就可以賺大錢了。"},{"pid":"325271d1c696a7dd00909bfdbd87fbca91ffa047","tid":2404312,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T17:27:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我的術式也是最近才發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}